# Active Directory Project 
This project demonstrates common Active directory (AD) tasks performed in a lab Environment , including creating and managing user accounts, resetting passwords, addingusers to security groups,
and joining computers to the domain. These tasks are relevent to IT help Desk Technician roles.

## Steps Performed
-Loged in to Active Directory users and computers 
-Opened the ADUC tool on the lab computer 

## Created and managed user accounts
-Added new users with details such as name, email, and department 
-edited and updated existing accounts.

## Reseted passwords and unlock user accounts.
-Reseted user passwords as needed.
-Unlocked accounts that were locked due to failed login attempts

## Group Management
-Added users to security and distribution groups
-Assigned permissions based on group membership

## Domain Mnagement
-Joined computers to the domain
-Verified domain connectivity and centralized management

## Tools Used
-Active Directory users and computers (ADUC)
-Windows Server / Windows Envorement 


